msgid "500:[name]梨深[line]「タク！」[%p]"
msgstr "500:[name]梨深[line]Taku![%p]"

msgid "600:僕を呼ぶ声。[%p]"
msgstr "600:A voice called me.[%p]"

msgid "700:振り返ると、梨深が階段を上がってきたところだった。[linebreak]彼女の制服姿を見るのは、あの日以来だ。[%p]"
msgstr "700:I turned around to see Rimi coming up the stairs. I hadn't seen her in her uniform since that day.[%p]"

msgid "800:梨深は僕に微笑みかけて、敬礼のようなポーズをした。[%p]"
msgstr "800:She smiled at me and gave me a salute.[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]梨深[line]「ビシィ！　おはよー」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]梨深[line]Snap! Good morning![%p]"

msgid "1000:[name]梨深[line]「朝ご飯、急いで作るね」[%p]"
msgstr "1000:[name]梨深[line]I'll make a quick breakfast, okay?[%p]"

msgid "1100:梨深の手には、コンビニの袋。[linebreak]中には食パンと卵、それに牛乳が入っていた。[linebreak]流し台の前に立ち、いそいそと準備を始める。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:She had a bag from the convenience store in her hands, with bread, eggs, and milk inside. She went over to the sink and started to cook.[%p]"

msgid "1200:梨深はこの２ヶ月、毎日のようにこのベースにやって来ては、ご飯を作ってくれている。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:She'd been coming over and making my meals every day for the past two months.[%p]"

msgid "1300:彼女自身は料理をろくにしたことがないらしくて、修行も兼ねているらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:She'd never really cooked before, she said, so this was her way of getting practice in.[%p]"

msgid "1400:僕を実験台にするなって言いたいけど、女の子の手料理を食べられるなんて幸せなことだから、あえてぐっと我慢していた。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:I wanted to tell her not to use me as a test subject, but it made me happy to eat a girl's homemade cooking, so I didn't say anything.[%p]"

msgid "1500:[name]梨深[line]「今日から学校、再開だね」[%p]"
msgstr "1500:[name]梨深[line]School starts today, huh?[%p]"

msgid "1600:あの地震以来、翠明学園はずっと休校になっていたけど、今日から再開する。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:Suimei Academy had been closed since the earthquake, and was finally reopening today.[%p]"

msgid "1700:これを機に、僕も半引きこもりのような生活はやめて、真面目に学校に行くことにしたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:I'd decided that this was the perfect time to quit my quasi-hikikomori life and start actually going to school.[%p]"

msgid "1800:[name]梨深[line]「タクと、また学校に通えるなんて、嬉しいな」[%p]"
msgstr "1800:[name]梨深[line]I'm happy I get to go to school with you again![%p]"

msgid "1900:卵を割りながら、梨深がそう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:Rimi cracked an egg as she spoke.[%p]"

msgid "2000:さすがに冬のまっただ中に外で食事するのは、寒さに耐えられなくて無理だ。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:It was too cold to eat outside in the middle of winter.[%p]"

msgid "2100:梨深が作ってくれた、２人分のトーストとスクランブルエッグを室内に運び、小さな座卓に並べる。[linebreak]それからソファに並んで座った。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:Rimi took the two plates of toast and scrambled eggs she'd made over to a small, low table. Then we both sat down on the sofa.[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]梨深[line]「じゃあ、いただきまーす」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]梨深[line]Okay, let's eat![%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]拓巳[line]「いただきます」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]拓巳[line]Let's eat![%p]"

msgid "2400:手を合わせてから、僕は座卓の端に置いてあったバターに手を伸ばす。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:We put our hands together, and then I stretched out my hand for the butter on the end of the table.[%p]"

