msgid "6000:[name]七海[line]「冗談だよ。本気にされても困っちゃうってば」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]七海[line]It was just a joke. Don't take me seriously![%p]"

msgid "6100:はあ……あんまりビックリさせるなよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:Hahh... Don't scare me like that.[%p]"

msgid "6200:３人で肩を並べて学校へ向かう。[linebreak]梨深は、ファンタズムのあの歌をまた鼻歌で奏でている。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:The three of us headed to school together. Rimi was humming that Phantasm song.[%p]"

msgid "6300:松濤公園の中を通り抜けるのが、僕がいつもしているショートカット。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:The three of us took the shortcut through Shoto Park, the one I always used.[%p]"

msgid "6400:公園は、池の石垣が一部崩れたままになっていたりと、地震の影響がわずかに見られる。それでも渋谷中心部の惨状に比べれば全然マシだった。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:There were still signs of the earthquake here in the park, like how part of the stone wall around the lake had fallen in. It was in great shape compared to the center of Shibuya, though.[%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]優愛[line]「おはようございます」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]優愛[line]Good morning.[%p]"

msgid "6600:優愛が、例のベンチに座っていた。[linebreak]僕らの方を振り返り、柔らかな笑みを浮かべて頭を下げてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:Yua was sitting on the bench where I always sat. She turned to me with a nod and a kind smile.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]優愛[line]「あの、西條くん、昨日は、とても楽しかったです」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]優愛[line]Um, Nishijo, I had a lot of fun yesterday.[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]七海[line]「昨日？」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]七海[line]Yesterday?[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]拓巳[line]「優愛と一緒に、秋葉原まで買い物に行ったんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]拓巳[line]I went shopping with Yua in Akihabara.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]七海[line]「あ、分かった。お人形さんでしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]七海[line]Oh, I know. Your dolls, right?[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]拓巳[line]「フィギュアと言えよぅ……」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]拓巳[line]They're not dolls, they're figures.[%p]"

msgid "7200:まあ、フィギュアを買いに行ったのは事実だけど。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:But yeah, we did go buy figures.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]優愛[line]「新しい星来ちゃん、さっそく、部屋に飾りました」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]優愛[line]I put my new Seira up in my room.[%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]梨深[line]「あたしも行きたかったなあ」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]梨深[line]I wish I could've gone.[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]拓巳[line]「え、梨深って、フィギュアに、興味あるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]拓巳[line]Huh? Rimi, you like anime figures?[%p]"

msgid "7600:すると梨深は、かすかにはにかんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:Rimi gave me a little smile.[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]梨深[line]「んー、っていうか」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]梨深[line]Hmm... more like...[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]梨深[line]「タクの好きなもの、あたしも、好きになりたいし」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]梨深[line]I want to like the things you like.[%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]七海[line]「わあ、大胆発言……」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]七海[line]Wow, a bold statement.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]優愛[line]「だったら、今度、一緒に買いに行きましょう」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]優愛[line]Why don't we all go shopping together some time, then?[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]梨深[line]「え、本当？　ありがとうございます」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]梨深[line]Huh? Really? Thank you.[%p]"

msgid "8200:優愛と梨深は、すっかり意気投合していた。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:Yua and Rimi were good friends now.[%p]"

msgid "8300:優愛と七海とは別校舎なので、昇降口で別れる。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:Nanami and Yua had classes in a different building, so we said goodbye at the school entrance.[%p]"

msgid "8400:上履きに履き替えていると、背後から誰かが、僕の耳に息を吹きかけてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:As I was changing into my jacket, somebody blew on my ear.[%p]"

msgid "8500:ぞわり、と鳥肌が立ち、飛び退くようにして振り返る。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:I shivered and leapt back.[%p]"

