msgstr "8600:It was Ayase. She had her mouth puffed out, lips forming an “o.”[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]あやせ[line]「ふふふ。おはよう、拓巳」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]あやせ[line]Heheheh... Good morning, Takumi.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、おはよう……」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]拓巳[line]Oh, good morning.[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]梨深[line]「おはよう、アヤちゃん」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]梨深[line]Good morning, Aya![%p]"

msgid "9000:[name]あやせ[line]「アヤちゃん……」[%p]"
msgstr "9000:[name]あやせ[line]Aya...[%p]"

msgid "9100:あやせは梨深の呼びかけにふと首を傾げ――[%p]"
msgstr "9100:Ayase seemed a little bewildered by what Rimi had called her.[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]あやせ[line]「初めてよ。そんな呼び方をされたのは」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]あやせ[line]That's the first time that anybody's called me that.[%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]あやせ[line]「悪くないわ」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]あやせ[line]I like it.[%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]梨深[line]「でしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]梨深[line]Right?[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]あやせ[line]「ファンタズムのライブがあるの。明後日」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]あやせ[line]Phantasm has a concert in two days.[%p]"

msgid "9600:いきなり話題が飛ぶ。[linebreak]あやせは相変わらずつかみ所がない。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:The conversation suddenly jumped to a new topic. Ayase was still as hard to follow as ever.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]あやせ[line]「よかったら来て」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]あやせ[line]I'd be glad if you came.[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]拓巳[line]「僕に言ってるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]拓巳[line]Are you saying this to me?[%p]"

msgid "9900:[name]あやせ[line]「拓巳に言ってるのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "9900:[name]あやせ[line]I'm saying this to you.[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]あやせ[line]「それと、梨深も」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]あやせ[line]And Rimi, too.[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]梨深[line]「わ、本当？　絶対行くね」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]梨深[line]Huh? Really? I'll definitely go![%p]"

msgid "10200:ファンタズムは一度解散したけど、今年に入って急遽復活したって聞いた。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Phantasm had split up, but I'd heard they suddenly reformed this year.[%p]"

msgid "10300:どういう心境の変化か分からないけど、あやせの歌はもう一度聞いてみたい。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:I didn't know what had prompted the change, but I wanted to hear Ayase sing again.[%p]"

