msgstr "11400:Kozupii charged down the hallway at me with a dazzling smile on her face.[%p]"

msgid "11500:でも教室から出てきた男子と激突し、派手に尻餅をつく。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:But she collided with a boy who was coming out of the classroom and landed hard on her butt.[%p]"

msgid "11600:こずぴぃは涙目になりながらその男子に謝り、それからやっとのことで僕のところへやって来た。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:She apologized to him with tears in her eyes, and then finally made it to me.[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]梢[line]「おはようさんさーんなの……」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]梢[line]Good morning.[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]梨深[line]「怪我はない？　廊下を走っちゃダメだよ、こずぴぃ」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]梨深[line]Are you hurt? Don't run in the hallways, Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]梢[line]「うにゅ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]梢[line]Unyuh...[%p]"

msgid "12000:こずぴぃはモジモジとした。[linebreak]それから上目遣いで僕の顔を見つめてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:She was fidgeting. She looked up into my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんに、はやーく教えたかったのら」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]梢[line]I wanted to be the first one to tell you![%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]拓巳[line]「教えるって、なにを？」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]拓巳[line]Tell me what?[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]梢[line]「うんとね、"
msgstr "12300:[name]梢[line]Um..."

msgid "12400:ほらっ！」[%p]"
msgstr "12400: Look![%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]梢[line]「うんとね、ほらっ！」"
msgstr "12500:[name]梢[line]Um... Look!"

msgid "12600:こずぴぃが、たった今自分が走ってきた方を指差す。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:Kozupii pointed in the direction she'd just been running from.[%p]"

msgid "12700:よく見ると、壁に寄りかかるようにして、セナが立っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:I looked again and saw Sena, leaning up against a wall.[%p]"

msgid "12800:腕を組み、やたらと不機嫌そうな表情を顔に貼り付けている。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:She had her arms crossed and an annoyed expression on her face.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]梨深[line]「セナさん、退院したんだー」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]梨深[line]Oh, Sena got out of the hospital![%p]"

msgid "13000:セナはこの２ヶ月、ずっと入院していた。[linebreak]諏訪にやられた精神攻撃をずっと引きずっていたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:Sena had been in the hospital the past two months. Suwa's psychological attacks had done lasting damage.[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "13200:セナは顔を上げると、僕らの方へとゆっくりと歩み寄ってきた。[linebreak]相変わらず怖い。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Sena looked up and slowly walked toward me. She was as scary as ever.[%p]"

msgid "13300:なんにもしてないのにいきなりビンタをかましてきそうな、そんなオーラをまとっている。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:She had a kind of air about her that suggested she might smack you across the face for no reason at all.[%p]"

msgid "13400:僕は週に二度はセナのお見舞いに行っていたけど、どれだけこっちが話を振っても、結局最後まで一言も口を利いてくれなかったなあ。あれは拷問にも似た気まずさだった。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:I'd gone to see her in the hospital twice a week, but no matter how much I'd tried to talk to her, she'd never said a single word to me. It was painfully, horribly, awkward.[%p]"

msgid "13500:もしかしたら激しく嫌われているのかもしれない。[linebreak]セナは、苦手だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:Maybe she hated me. Or maybe Sena was just an intimidating person…[%p]"

msgid "13600:僕とセナの間に流れる、張り詰めた緊張感。[linebreak]というか一方的に僕がビビってるだけなんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:The air grew tense between the two of us. Or maybe it was just that I was scared.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]梢[line]「というわーけで！　今日学校が終わったら、退院のおいわーいをしよしよっ」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]梢[line]And so...! Once school's over, let's have a party to celebrate![%p]"

msgid "13800:こずぴぃひとりだけが、はしゃいだ様子を見せる。[linebreak]こ、この雰囲気でお祝いもクソもないような気が……。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:Kozupii was extremely excited. But Sena certainly didn't look like she wanted to celebrate…[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]セナ[line]「おい、西條」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]セナ[line]You. Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "14000:そこでようやくセナが口を開いた。[linebreak]ギクッとする。目を合わせられない。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:For the first time, Sena spoke. I shivered. I couldn't look her in the eye.[%p]"

msgid "14100:[name]セナ[line]「これを」[%p]"
msgstr "14100:[name]セナ[line]Here.[%p]"

msgid "14200:と、セナがなにかを差し出してきた。[linebreak]それは“あたり”と書かれた小さな棒。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:Sena offered me something. It was a small stick marked “winner.”[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]拓巳[line]「……？」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]拓巳[line]...?[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]梢[line]「あ、ガルガリ君の当たり棒なのら」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]梢[line]Oh, it's a winning Garugari-kun stick, nora![%p]"

msgid "14500:困惑しつつ、それを受け取った。[linebreak]セナはすぐにプイとそっぽを向き。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:I took it from her, a little confused. Sena gave me a “hmph” and looked away.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]セナ[line]「お前に、言いたいことがある」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]セナ[line]There's something I want to tell you.[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なんでしょう……？」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]拓巳[line]W-What is it?[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14900:なんだか、セナの頬が桜色に染まっているように見えるのは気のせいだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:For some reason, her cheeks looked flushed. Or was I imagining things?[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]セナ[line]「お、お前のことが……好きだ」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]セナ[line]I-I'm... in love with you.[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]拓巳[line]「…………へ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "15300:[name]梢[line]「うぴ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]梢[line]Upiih?[%p]"

msgid "15400:いきなりの告白に、僕だけじゃなくて梨深もこずぴぃもぽか〜んとしてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Her sudden confession startled not just me, but Kozupii and Rimi as well.[%p]"

msgid "15500:一瞬、からかわれたかと思ったけど、セナはそんな冗談を言うキャラじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I thought for a moment that maybe she was just messing with me, but Sena didn't tell jokes like that.[%p]"

msgid "15600:ということは……ｍｊｄ？[%p]"
msgstr "15600:So... mjd?[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]セナ[line]「何度も、お見舞いに来てくれて……嬉しかったんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]セナ[line]I was so happy when you came to see me in the hospital.[%p]"

msgid "15800:[name]セナ[line]「い、言わせるな、このバカが！」[%p]"
msgstr "15800:[name]セナ[line]D-Don't make me say it aloud, you jerk![%p]"

msgid "15900:勝手にデレて、勝手にツンに戻っている。[linebreak]いやしかし、いきなりそんなこと言われても……[%p]"
msgstr "15900:She went from tsun to dere, and then back to tsun. But still, this was all so sudden...[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]梨深[line]「ええええええ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]梨深[line]HUHHH?![%p]"

msgid "16100:ワンテンポ遅れて、梨深が驚きの声をあげる。[linebreak]こずぴぃはまだ状況を理解していないのか、目を白黒させている。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:There was a beat, and then Rimi yelled in surprise. Kozupii was blinking her eyes in shock, seemingly unable to understand what was going on.[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]セナ[line]「なんだ、咲畑。異論があるのか」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]セナ[line]Oh, Sakihata. You have a problem with that?[%p]"

msgid "16300:[name]梨深[line]「ありまくりだよっ！　そんな、えーとえーと、と、とにかくダメだって！」[%p]"
msgstr "16300:[name]梨深[line]Of course I do! It's um, um... W-Well, it's just not right![%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]梢[line]「？？？？」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]梢[line]????[%p]"

msgid "16500:梨深やこずぴぃは激しく混乱しているけど、一番困惑してるのは僕だよ。[linebreak]まさかそんな宣言されるなんて。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:Rimi and Kozupii were totally confused, but I was the most confused person of all. I couldn't believe what I was hearing.[%p]"

msgid "16600:いったいどんなリアクションを取ればいいのか分からなくて、僕は窓の外の、透明な空を見上げた。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I looked up at the clear sky outside the window, unsure of how to react.[%p]"

msgid "16700:なんだか、新学期が始まって早々、ドタバタした１日になったなあ。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:It was only the first day of school, and so many fun things had happened already.[%p]"

msgid "16800:この平穏で、楽しくなりそうな時間が、これから毎日のように続くんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:Would these peaceful, happy days last forever?[%p]"

msgid "16900:――続いてほしいな。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:—I hoped so.[%p]"

msgid "17000:僕は心からそう願って。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:I really, really did.[%p]"

msgid "17100:ふと、窓に映った自分の顔を見た。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:And then, suddenly, I saw myself reflected in the window.[%p]"

msgid "17200:そこに映っているのは。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:But what I saw...[%p]"

msgid "17300:僕じゃなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:wasn't me.[%p]"

msgid "17400:皺だらけの――[%p]"
msgstr "17400:It was an old man with wrinkled skin.[%p]"

msgid "17500:色が、光が、消えた。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:The color and the light disappeared.[%p]"

msgid "17600:僕は真っ暗な空間で、膝を抱えている。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:I was sitting on the ground in a dark space, hands wrapped around my knees.[%p]"

msgid "17700:目の前には、この空間の唯一の光源。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:In front of me was the only source of light.[%p]"

msgid "17800:モニタのような、窓のような、枠のようなもの。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:It was like a monitor... or a window, or a frame.[%p]"

msgid "17900:その中で、梨深と、セナと、こずぴぃが、楽しそうになにかを喋っている。声は聞こえてこない。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:Inside it, Rimi and Sena and Kozupii were laughing and talking. I couldn't hear what they were saying.[%p]"

msgid "18000:それを見つめる僕は。[linebreak]感情が完璧に凪いでいて。[linebreak]あるいは、心が死んでいるのかもしれなくて。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:As I looked at it, I didn't feel anything at all. Perhaps my mind had been destroyed.[%p]"

msgid "18100:気付く。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:Suddenly, I realized...[%p]"

msgid "18200:見ていたのは、僕の妄想。[linebreak]逃げ込んだ、二次元の世界。[linebreak]完全なる幻。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:what I'd been seeing was my delusion. A 2D world that I'd escaped into. A total hallucination.[%p]"

msgid "18300:いつから、妄想だった？[%p]"
msgstr "18300:How much of it was a delusion?[%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]野呂瀬[line]「最初からですよ」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]野呂瀬[line]All of it.[%p]"

msgid "18500:背後を振り向く。[linebreak]野呂瀬が立っていた。[linebreak]でも暗くて、足しか見えない。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:I turned around. Norose was standing there, but it was so dark that I could only see his feet.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]野呂瀬[line]「諏訪くんに、心を殺されたではありませんか」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]野呂瀬[line]Suwa destroyed your mind, didn't he?[%p]"

msgid "18700:あのときから、ずっと、僕は妄想を……？[%p]"
msgstr "18700:So, everything after that was a delusion?[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]野呂瀬[line]「君のＣＯＤＥサンプルは採取できました。もう用済みですから、いつでも塵に還ってもらって結構です」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]野呂瀬[line]We have your CODE sample now. We're finished with you. Feel free to die at your own convenience.[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "19000:なにも感じない。[linebreak]心が死んだんだから。[linebreak]なにも感じないはずなのに。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:I didn't feel a thing. My mind had been destroyed. I shouldn't have been able to feel a thing…[%p]"

msgid "19100:一筋、涙が頬をつたった。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:but for some reason, a single tear ran down my cheek.[%p]"

msgid "19200:僕は、最後の最後で、負け犬に戻ったんだ。辛い現実から、逃げたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:At the very end of everything, I'd turned back into a loser. I'd tried to run from a painful reality.[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]野呂瀬[line]「最後に幸せな夢を見られて、よかったですね」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]野呂瀬[line]I'm glad you were able to have a happy dream before the end.[%p]"

msgid "19400:僕は、結局、価値のない人間だった。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:At the very end of everything, I'd turned out to be totally worthless.[%p]"

msgid "19500:ごめん、梨深。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:I'm sorry, Rimi.[%p]"

msgid "19600:謝っても、なぜ謝らなくちゃいけないのか、もうよく分からなくなっていた。[linebreak]罪悪感も、感じなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:I apologized, but I didn't even know anymore why I had to apologize. I didn't feel any guilt.[%p]"

msgid "19700:そして僕は、さっきの妄想の続きに戻ることにした。[linebreak]そのうち、誰かが僕のことを殺してくれるだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:I decided to go back to the delusion I'd been enjoying. Eventually, somebody would come along to kill me.[%p]"

msgid "19800:だからそれまで、逃避した世界で幸せに浸りたかった。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:Until that happened, I wanted to immerse myself in the happiness of the false world I'd escaped into.[%p]"

